[img]http://www.upload.ee/image/643535/212flop.png[/img]
First of all story, idc if you dont read it or care: Generation-X were a succesfully server made 2009 december, A guy named Mystic foe joined their server. It got very famous on Rune L0cos + my coding. Some months later we got 200+ players online, but there was a big problem a stupid fag/idiot/ well come on gen-x he was old donator and he ddosed/hacked/got 50+ hidden admin accounts ect...We got less players we came back after a while, we had around 50+ players, some days later he cames back, i got very bored on gen-x there was no meant to be there. There were about 10 - 30 players ya only ppl who i known'd played. i quited the server they got angry cuz their server were dead. I dediced to make a server self got 50+ 2 days of running, we got 220 votes what exactly happends? Ye ilikil gave my Rune L0cos page to Generation-X like wut? I got banned from Rune L0cos ;s, So ya this is Generation-X Release.
^ Sad story.
Generation-X Features: Magic Formula. Perfect Switching. Much dupes fixed, but ya some left. Dragon claws + i changed the hits. Trade ^ Perfect Hybriding. Now to a good part: Using Graham's Event mangar, it is used wrong but ya it works. We got working Friend list, Much map datas. Alot of needed commands. 2nd server with turmoil/ss. I dont know if soul split effect is added, but ya.., I dont really remember. New Packed.. Bountyhunter bugged, worked with it 5 - 10 mins, Shahir's base.
Many more features....

ye dont care about my packing..
